data.description: This wonderful home is majestically situated on an expansive, one-acre estate that truly offers the best value in the area. Exceptional amenities await you, including not one, but TWO STATE OF THE ART SHOP BUILDINGS tailored for the modern hobbyist, entrepreneur, or DIY enthusiast! The first workshop is an expansive 30x30 space, boasting 10-foot overhead doors for easy access to all your projects. With solid concrete floors, 220-volt electrical capabilities, and an adjoining carport, it’s the ultimate workspace that fulfills every craftsman’s wish list. The second shop is equally impressive; it's a generous 21x21 space equipped with concrete floors, an 8-foot overhead door, and 220-volt electricity, ensuring you have all you need for your endeavors, large or small. As you step inside the main residence, you’re welcomed by newly installed tile flooring that graces the entryway, kitchen, and an incredibly versatile flex room. This multi-purpose area is perfect for a home office, or it could effortlessly convert into a cozy third bedroom—your choice! To further enhance your peace of mind, the home features a high-efficiency HVAC system, updated within the last two years, well pump installed in 2021, front carport installed this year at a cost of $4,000! Plus, safeguard your investment with a brand-new, hail-resistant shingle roof, installed as recently as 2021.
